HEADWORD: Loevens larva
<hw>Loev"en's lar"va</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Named after
the Swedish Zoologist, <person>S. F. <etsep>L⟦oum⟧ven</etsep></person>,
who discovered it.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The peculiar larva of
